abstract: Target reduces by half its minimum online purchase to qualify for free shipping on most orders, to $25.
lead_paragraph: Target has reduced by half its minimum online purchase to qualify for free shipping on most orders, to $25, taking aim at competitors Walmart and Amazon, both of which have higher minimums.

headline.main: Target Offers Free Delivery on Online Orders Over $25
headline.print_headline: Target Offers Free Delivery on Online Orders Over $25
